snippet.title: Catlateral Damage Infomercial
snippet.description:
Are you tired of your cat having all the fun? Do you just want to cat? WELL NOW YOU CAN CAT... WITH CATLATERAL DAMAGE!

Catlateral Damage comes to Steam and OUYA in late May 2015. Play as a cat on a rampage trying to knock over everything before your human gets home. 

For more information check out
www.catlateraldamage.com
http://store.steampowered.com/app/329860/
